node.text: This one really hit home for us 😊 We received this amazing video from a very long time family member @elcropal ❤️ He has kept every thank you card we have sent him with every package he has received and that’s not a small number ❤️ Thankful for everyone that supports us each and every day and keeps the dream alive 🧑‍🚀🚀

Nothing better than some accessories 😍👀 @los1glass dropping some heaters tonight 😎🤘 See everyone there in store at 6PM(est) then join us at 7:10PM(est) on our @planetcaravandrops page for our live showcase 🤩❤️ Finally make your scoops at 8:10PM(est) on the website www.planetcaravansmokeshop.com 🤘💥 See everyone there and make sure to hit that DM if you have any questions 🧑‍🚀🚀

node.text: RAGER ALERT 🚨😍 These @los1glass “trigs” have that nice chop function you are looking for in a tube 🤯🌲 Wanted to really show that off so we decided to display one of the clears that we will have available tonight for the @los1glass drop 👀🤩 See everyone there and make sure to shoot over a DM if you have any questions 🧑‍🚀🚀

Let’s get natural 🌲😎 @los1glass making it easy to be one with nature with his beautiful “trig” tubes 😍👀 We will have these in full color and clear dropping tonight! 🤩🔥 This one is in the color “Lucid” and pops super hard in the sun ☀️💥 We will also have some bubble caps and pendys dropping that will be shown off soon so stay posted 🧑‍🚀🚀

node.text: When’s the last time you used a gum ball machine? Let these @wheeler_glass take you back to a simpler time when there was a gym ball machine on every corner 😊💥 These super unique gum ball bubble caps and pendys are easily the most fun thing that has came in the shop 🥳🔥 We will have these available tonight at 8:10PM(est) on the website www.planetcaravansmokeshop.com and will be showing them off at 7:10PM(est) tonight live on our @planetcaravandrops page 🧑‍🚀🚀
